ector on the other hand eleazar gómez zapata was appointed director of pemex cogeneración y servicios gómez zapata acted as deputy director of maintenance coordination of the corporate direction of operations which transformed into corporate direction of planning coordination and performance in addition rodulfo figueroa alonso who acted as deputy director of planning of pemex gas and basic petrochemicals was appointed as the new corporate director of planning coordination and performance las menciones de pemex pueden referirse a petróleos mexicanos o a cualquiera de sus empresas productivas subsidiarias última modificación   pemex consejo limitation of liabilitycontacthelpprivacydirectory  petróleos mexicanos marina nacional  col petróleos mexicanos cp  méxico df     ifai  portal de obligaciones de transparencia  infomex nuevo pemex cogeneration power plant tabasco  power technology project type gasfired cogeneration power plant location villahermosa tabasco mexico installed capacity mw ownership abengoa  ge energy financial services  epc contractors abener and abengoa méxico order year  completion  the mw cogeneration power plant is located at the nuevo pemex gas processing facility near villahermosa tabasco mexico the nuevo pemex cogeneration plant will supply electricity and steam to the adjacent gas processing facility of pemex ge supplied two fa gas turbines for the nuevo pemex cogeneration plant the nuevo pemex cogeneration plant was inaugurated by the mexican president in october  nuevo pemex cogeneration power plant tabasco mexico the mw nuevo pemex cogeneration power plant the largest of its kind in mexico was inaugurated in october  it is coowned by abengoa  and ge energy financial services it is located at the nuevo pemex gas processing facility near villahermosa tabasco which is owned by petróleos mexicanos pemex mexicos stateowned company that extracts and processes oil and gasthe nuevo pemex cogeneration power plant will provide energy to meet the enti